{"tid":1955902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【新冠肺炎】3外國人插隊檢測　青島嶗山區衛生局回應：深表歉意","createTime":"2020-04-02T20:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T01:42:40.000Z","uid":224066,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"99ca9fbedc9c99858e2246fb6f04cdd2b8278368","tid":1955902,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T20:28:49.000Z","msg":"山東省青島市嶗山區一間社區衛生服務中心，周三（4月1日）在市民排隊接受檢測期間，3名外國人被發現插隊，有其他排隊人上前理論，雙方爆發衝突；嶗山區衞生局其後在微博向公眾致歉，強調會做好秩序管理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4254688/org/921bd60b9cade1a60aead8efca637cf5.jpg/gDlXp0uciy4yEuS7X3YPZjIiJlww2JDuIZEn0CGRJ9A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4254688%2Forg%2F921bd60b9cade1a60aead8efca637cf5.jpg%2FgDlXp0uciy4yEuS7X3YPZjIiJlww2JDuIZEn0CGRJ9A&h=7fbc954e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4254677/org/d73360a8f2ac5f368c6b83de58fb0f12.jpg/nqGfrIPB0Y6Uvdm7LiNKNDHpgqirIKp9aei9N2novTc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4254677%2Forg%2Fd73360a8f2ac5f368c6b83de58fb0f12.jpg%2FnqGfrIPB0Y6Uvdm7LiNKNDHpgqirIKp9aei9N2novTc&h=fab5f461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上片段顯示，一名身穿黑色外套的男子在排隊等候檢測期間，發現3名外國人插隊，於是上前欲與對方理論，豈料其中一名穿灰色外套的外籍男子突然走過來，搶去他手中的單據扔到地上，且大叫：「中國人出去」（Chinese get out），當場引起現場其他人士不滿，「他們（現場工作人員）說『給個面子，外國人可以不排隊』，然後我們在這裏等了那麼久，然後外國人就直接插隊。為甚麼他們（外國人）就可以（不排隊）？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4254689/org/917174a5867214bba321852056c286d0.jpg/w-pIGa1HMq6v3LylqqIgjjQsO-ynPilEl1VqwpdVasI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4254689%2Forg%2F917174a5867214bba321852056c286d0.jpg%2Fw-pIGa1HMq6v3LylqqIgjjQsO-ynPilEl1VqwpdVasI&h=5406cd1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4254678/org/1f9171a4b99403c61e4596dd14e64e10.jpg/9mAmCygziMGkf-pNS2Eg1hndLSqP0qPRc3w0dXN8NHU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4254678%2Forg%2F1f9171a4b99403c61e4596dd14e64e10.jpg%2F9mAmCygziMGkf-pNS2Eg1hndLSqP0qPRc3w0dXN8NHU&h=6b3fec3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該服務中心的工作人員其後表示，檢測工作不是由他們進行，中心只負責提供場地；嶗山區衞生局在微博回應稱，因為排隊的人較多，因此出現插隊情況，並為引起民眾不滿致歉，將會加強管理和維持秩序。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起網民不滿，留言稱「為什麼洋人可以胡作非為，中國公民只能忍氣吞聲」、「歸根究底就是那個工作人員的錯！他要是嚴厲的讓他們（外國人）排隊，就不會發生這件事」、「什麼年代了？還讓外國人優先？有病吧！」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VmeqgB7vxrs&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVmeqgB7vxrs%26feature%3Demb_logo&h=4829cc68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k96J0Ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk96J0Ee.jpg&h=bdb95ffb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30cbb1d69487eea8e961496a7352e67998d049f8","tid":1955902,"uid":34534,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T22:47:53.000Z","msg":"韭菜黎架咋你地"},{"pid":"5319fdeed93c59cec7e4075f752efd91e1321a1e","tid":1955902,"uid":145326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T22:52:46.000Z","msg":"Chinese get out<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b751ebf0d7c31acf78aa08ad5eb0e7d98ca3538","tid":1955902,"uid":321837,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T22:53:04.000Z","msg":"咁呢個時候仲留係你中國的，一定係支共的好朋友，WHO譚德塞之流。相對嚟講，你們只算個屁"},{"pid":"76e8f8e237297639145fcfa9abf43d2ec331b729","tid":1955902,"uid":312333,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T22:55:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新你老母，武漢肺炎呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"61069d8c4351253ae4191d03c2b5f5d798c4e49b","tid":1955902,"uid":32263,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T23:00:57.000Z","msg":"唔排隊融入你地文化姐大家都係中國人"},{"pid":"8ffacc9e722cf6fdd197ac106a980